THEORY Sum2Lists

IMPORT-THEORY Equality
IMPORT-THEORY Arithmetic
IMPORT-THEORY List
IMPORT-HASKELL List

THEOREM sum_lists_42_99

    sum ((42:[])++(99:[]))  ==  sum (42:99:[]) + sum []

STRATEGY ReduceAll


  sum ((42:[])++(99:[]))  ==  sum (42:99:[]) + sum []

  
  END ReduceAll

QED sum_lists_42_99
